help.timeFormat: Format string for displaying time labels (e.g., 'hh:mm a'). Supported tokens: YYYY (4-digit year), YY (2-digit year), MM (2-digit month), M (month), DD (2-digit day), D (day), hh (2-digit 12-hour), h (12-hour), HH (2-digit 24-hour), H (24-hour), mm (2-digit minutes), m (minutes), a (am/pm), A (AM/PM).
